headline: KeyCorp (KEY): Assessing Valuation After Q3 2025 Profit Recovery and Strategic Execution
summary: KeyCorp (KEY) has delivered a turnaround in the third quarter of 2025, returning to profitability after last year's loss. The comeback is tied to tighter control of interest expenses and higher noninterest income. This signals effective navigation of tougher conditions for regional banks.
